    <section name="Release Notes of 3.x">
      <subsection name="3.0.2">
        <ul>
          <li>[<a href='https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPFORGE-291'>HIPFORGE-291</a>] -         [Gallery Magick] Add -size option and +profile option for better performance
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="3.0.1">
        <ul>
          <li>[<a href='https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPFORGE-273'>HIPFORGE-273</a>] -         [Gallery Magick] Make the handling of zero dimensions same as Hippo Gallery's default behavior
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="3.0.0">
        <ul>
          <li>[<a href='https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPFORGE-253'>HIPFORGE-253</a>] -         [Gallery Magick] Upgrade for v13 compatibility
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
    </section>
    <section name="Release Notes of 2.x">
      <subsection name="2.0.2">
        <ul>
          <li>[<a href='https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPFORGE-273'>HIPFORGE-273</a>] -         [Gallery Magick] Make the handling of zero dimensions same as Hippo Gallery's default behavior
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="2.0.1">
        <ul>
          <li>[<a href='https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPFORGE-183'>HIPFORGE-183</a>] -         [Gallery Magick] Extract and store image metadata extractable through identify command
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="2.0.0">
        <ul>
          <li>
            Compliant with Hippo CMS 12.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
    </section>
    <section name="Release Notes of 1.x">
      <subsection name="1.0.6">
        <ul>
          <li>[<a href='https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-1394'>HIPPLUG-1394</a>] -         Gallery Magick: Make external process unblocking
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.0.5">
        <ul>
          <li>
            Supporting pure Java image resizing processor utility, <code>org.onehippo.forge.gallerymagick.core.command.ScalrProcessorUtils</code>,
            using Scalr library which is used by Hippo CMS Gallery Processor as well.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.0.4">
        <ul>
          <li>
            Exposing system property, org.onehippo.forge.gallerymagick.core.command.im.identify.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.0.3">
        <ul>
          <li>
            Bug fix: close the file input stream of the original file.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.0.2">
        <ul>
          <li>
            Supports Magick Command Gallery Processor Plugin.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.0.1">
        <ul>
          <li>
            Supports utility to identify dimension of image file.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="1.0.0">
        <ul>
          <li>
            Initial release.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
    </section>
